rComments: Professor Kim is one of the most memorable professors I've had from my undergraduate career in architecture. She is clear about her requirements, and her grades match up with her feedback; which really matters. Deliver what is expected from you and she will reward you. She is also very easy to speak to and is very helpful despite her busy schedule.
Amazing professor!  I found her feedback very helpful. She is also very supportive of her students, and gives them enough space to explore their interests.
She's great and her course helped me improve so much. So glad I had her as my prof

Incredibly intelligent, passionate and caring teacher hampered by lecture style. Be ready to write fast and miss many points due to the speed and density of the lecture material. But what you do come out with is well articulated and thought provoking.

I tried hard to find some sort of saving grace with this class because I'm passionate about the topics and I think Professor Kim is an amazing person. However, the readings and the lecture are unintelligible. I wish that she would spend the lectures translating the readings for us instead of confusing us even more.
